### Phase 1 – Backend

#### [NEW] [server.js](file:///Users/mutz/Documents/14%20-%20Vibecoding/KV-Efz/server/server.js)
Express app entry point: CORS, JSON parsing, route mounting, MongoDB connection via Mongoose.

#### [NEW] Models: `User.js`, `Question.js`, `Session.js`, `FlashcardDeck.js`
- **User**: email, passwordHash, name, role (user/admin), isPremium, streak, lastActive, googleId
- **Question**: text, type (mcq/truefalse/fillblank), options[], correctAnswer, explanation, topic, subtopic, difficulty
- **Session**: userId, type (quiz/exam), questions[], answers[], score, duration, completedAt
- **FlashcardDeck**: topic, cards[{front, back}]

#### [NEW] Routes: `auth.js`, `questions.js`, `sessions.js`, `progress.js`, `payment.js`
- **Auth**: POST `/register`, `/login`, `/google`, GET `/me`
- **Questions**: Full CRUD (admin-only for write), GET with filters (topic, difficulty, type)
- **Sessions**: POST create session, PUT submit answers, GET user sessions
- **Progress**: GET stats (avg score, streak, topic mastery, history)
- **Payment**: POST create Stripe checkout, webhook for payment confirmation

#### [NEW] Middleware: `auth.js`, `admin.js`
JWT verification + admin role check.

#### [NEW] Seed data: `questions.json`, `flashcards.json`
~250 realistic German MCQ/TF/fill-blank questions across 6 topics + flashcard decks.

